      "content": "it really does feel like an escape. i just keep thinking about how much more peaceful it would be if i didn't have to wake up to this every morning. people talk about \"fighting\" and \"strength,\" but sometimes it feels like fighting is just prolonging the agony. isn't it a bit cruel to expect someone to just endure this kind of torture indefinitely? it feels like the only way to actually find peace is to just... let go.",
